It's fine that he's a commoner,

666
00:35:04,900 --> 00:35:07,500
but you listened to him

667
00:35:07,820 --> 00:35:09,780
and cut off the noble families
from the Crown Prince.

668
00:35:13,420 --> 00:35:15,780
Your Highness, I'd like to ask you

669
00:35:16,300 --> 00:35:18,500
why you're doing

670
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:21,180
all this.

671
00:35:23,420 --> 00:35:26,500
For the sake of making the son
of that humble woman, Consort Rou,

672
00:35:26,500 --> 00:35:28,020
ascend the throne?

673
00:35:34,420 --> 00:35:35,900
All Her Highness has done

674
00:35:37,380 --> 00:35:39,260
is to stop people like you

675
00:35:40,380 --> 00:35:42,660
from asking why.

676
00:35:47,060 --> 00:35:48,380
What she seeks in the world

677
00:35:48,900 --> 00:35:50,780
is not for the family
to be the most important

678
00:35:51,740 --> 00:35:54,820
but for all people to live a happy life

679
00:35:55,020 --> 00:35:56,140
with hope.

680
00:35:57,940 --> 00:35:59,260
It may not be realized today.

681
00:35:59,780 --> 00:36:02,100
It may not be realized
in a hundred years or a thousand years.

682
00:36:02,780 --> 00:36:04,500
But Her Highness still hopes

683
00:36:04,780 --> 00:36:05,860
that one day

684
00:36:06,220 --> 00:36:08,060
there will be no more people like you

685
00:36:08,300 --> 00:36:10,020
asking what you did wrong,

686
00:36:10,860 --> 00:36:12,780
and no more people like you

687
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:16,860
accusing Her Highness of being a royal
descendant married to a commoner.

688
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:26,460
Pei Wenxuan has already

689
00:36:28,260 --> 00:36:30,420
answered your question.

690
00:36:31,820 --> 00:36:35,060
You can leave in peace on your journey.

691
00:36:46,500 --> 00:36:47,260
Mr. Su.

692
00:36:49,100 --> 00:36:50,260
If there's nothing else,

693
00:36:51,260 --> 00:36:52,820
we'll be going.

694
00:36:53,340 --> 00:36:53,980
Your Highness.

695
00:36:55,140 --> 00:36:55,660
Please.

696
00:37:09,260 --> 00:37:13,540
The biggest mistake
in Mr. Xie's life

697
00:37:13,940 --> 00:37:15,900
is that he shouldn't have allowed
himself to be carried away

698
00:37:16,980 --> 00:37:18,060
even if he was deeply in love.

699
00:37:22,340 --> 00:37:23,900
Are you the same?

700
00:37:26,660 --> 00:37:28,260
In your world,

701
00:37:28,820 --> 00:37:29,980
you can even

702
00:37:30,220 --> 00:37:31,980
kill your beloved
for the sake of your family?

703
00:37:38,780 --> 00:37:39,500
Why are you saying

704
00:37:39,500 --> 00:37:41,100
such an unfortunate thing
out of the blue?

705
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:43,340
I'm just asking.

706
00:37:43,740 --> 00:37:45,100
Mr. Su won't mind.

707
00:37:45,340 --> 00:37:46,180
I do mind.

708
00:37:48,540 --> 00:37:49,740
Mr. Pei,

709
00:37:50,260 --> 00:37:52,060
please don't make fun of my beloved.

710
00:37:56,340 --> 00:37:58,820
Mr. Su, do you have a beloved?

711
00:38:01,740 --> 00:38:06,060
♪It's like standing on the edge
of a bottomless abyss♪

712
00:38:06,060 --> 00:38:07,900
Yes or no...

713
00:38:09,660 --> 00:38:12,420
it's not something
you should make fun of.

714
00:38:12,420 --> 00:38:16,100
♪But here,
the blossoms you adore abound♪

715
00:38:17,660 --> 00:38:18,900
I'm sorry for speaking out of turn.

716
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:21,220
♪How do I shout out the words
I want to say?♪

717
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:24,460
But you haven't addressed me

718
00:38:24,660 --> 00:38:26,780
as Your Highness, have you?

719
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:30,500
♪But the wind in the valley
gently ceases its whispers♪

720
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:32,140
Now, the prince consort's rank

721
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:34,200
