of the investigating censor

722
00:38:34,210 --> 00:38:35,380
of the Censorate.

723
00:38:35,740 --> 00:38:37,220
You come from a prestigious family,

724
00:38:37,260 --> 00:38:38,620
so you should abide by the rules.

725
00:38:39,580 --> 00:38:42,420
Don't make that mistake again.

726
00:38:42,420 --> 00:38:46,020
♪If we met at the right time,
love wouldn't have been so complicated♪

727
00:38:46,020 --> 00:38:46,820
Let's go, Your Highness.

728
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:49,260
Your Highness.

729
00:38:49,260 --> 00:38:51,220
♪The wind carries sand and dust♪

730
00:38:51,220 --> 00:38:54,820
♪The moment I see the sunset♪

731
00:38:54,820 --> 00:38:55,980
As the Chinese New Year is approaching,

732
00:38:56,460 --> 00:38:59,900
I would like to wish you
a happy Chinese New Year

733
00:39:00,220 --> 00:39:01,100
and all the best early.

734
00:39:01,580 --> 00:39:05,540
♪My world gradually falls apart
as we fail to understand each other♪

735
00:39:05,540 --> 00:39:08,180
Mr. Su, I also wish you
a happy Chinese New Year

736
00:39:08,460 --> 00:39:09,340
and a bright future.

737
00:39:13,020 --> 00:39:13,780
Thank you, Your Highness.

738
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:25,600
♪I can't bring myself
to take a step forward♪

739
00:39:25,600 --> 00:39:27,780
♪Fulfilling others is something great♪

740
00:39:27,780 --> 00:39:28,660
What's on your mind?

741
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:33,260
♪And there's no need to be afraid♪

742
00:39:33,940 --> 00:39:35,100
I think...

743
00:39:35,100 --> 00:39:36,300
♪Just go for it with guts♪

744
00:39:36,300 --> 00:39:37,380
