749
00:39:49,700 --> 00:39:53,320
♪You know I just want to shield you♪

750
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:55,920
♪From the chaos of the world♪

751
00:39:55,920 --> 00:39:58,220
♪The sound of falling rain is ticking♪

752
00:39:58,220 --> 00:39:59,540
I hope I'm overthinking this.

753
00:39:59,540 --> 00:40:01,580
♪Like the sound of a guqin
beating on fallen flowers♪

754
00:40:01,580 --> 00:40:02,260
Let's go.

