761
00:40:28,420 --> 00:40:29,180
But last time,

762
00:40:29,180 --> 00:40:31,540
Her Highness
and the Prince Consort ended so badly,

763
00:40:32,420 --> 00:40:33,580
why is she

764
00:40:34,060 --> 00:40:36,380
still with Pei Wenxuan this time?

765
00:40:39,420 --> 00:40:41,220
Is Pei Wenxuan back?

766
00:40:51,500 --> 00:40:52,300
This time,

767
00:40:53,020 --> 00:40:54,740
I have to protect both my family

768
00:40:55,260 --> 00:40:56,780
